sentences.english: I come over here to have classes three a week.

sentences.english: Yes. You can get off at Wudaokou.
sentences.chinese: 是的，你可以在五道口下。

sentences.english: The Wudaokou station is on the lightrail, so you’ll have to transfer.
sentences.chinese: 五道口地铁是轻轨站，所以你要转车。

sentences.english: The construction of Beijing University Wu Daokou student lodging house began in Beijing at the end of 2000.
sentences.chinese: 北京大学五道口学生公寓于2000年年底正式开工。

sentences.english: I make it back to Wudaokou in the late evening. I usually go to sleep by midnight.
sentences.chinese: 晚上，俺会走回五道口，并在午夜前睡觉。

sentences.english: I live in Wudaokou. I come over here to have classes three a week.
sentences.chinese: 我住在五道口，每周来这边上三次课。

sentences.english: I sleep on the ground under the bridge at the Wudaokou subway station.
sentences.chinese: 俺睡在五道口地铁站的桥地下。
